{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "internal": "softpeak", "icon": "SOP/softpeak", "tags": "reshape, model, normals", "version": null, "namespace": null}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Soft Peak"], "extent": [99, 113]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Moves the selected point along its normal, with smooth rolloff to\nsurrounding points."], "extent": [113, 207]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["Unlike the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/peak", "type": "link", "text": ["Peak node"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/peak.html"}, ",\nSoft Peak takes into account a rolloff function and a\nradius of influence. The points within radius distance to the selected\npoint or group will be displaced by an amount proportional to the distance,\nsimilar to the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/softxform", "type": "link", "text": ["Soft Transform node"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/softxform.html"}], "extent": [207, 504]}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [504, 516], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Group"], "extent": [516, 523], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Subset of points to translate."], "extent": [523, 558]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Distance"], "extent": [558, 568], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Distance along normal by which to translate."], "extent": [590, 639]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channels": "/dist"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Distance Metric"], "extent": [639, 656], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Method for measuring which points are within the soft radius."], "extent": [677, 744]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Edge"], "extent": [744, 754], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The shortest distance to a point in the group following a path along\n        edges."], "extent": [754, 846]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Surface"], "extent": [846, 859], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The shortest distance to a point in the group following a path\n        along the surface."], "extent": [859, 957]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Radius"], "extent": [957, 969], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The 3D distance to the closest point in the group."], "extent": [969, 1028]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Radius with Connectivity (deprecated)"], "extent": [1028, 1071], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The 3D distance to the closest point in the group, as long as there\n        is a connected path contained entirely within the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Soft Radius"]}, "."], "extent": [1071, 1222]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Attribute"], "extent": [1222, 1237], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": [{"type": "ui", "text": ["Lead Point Attribute"]}, " is used to determine which normal each\n        point should follow, and ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Distance Attribute"]}, " determines how\n        much each point is translated. Only points in the input group will\n        be translated, even if other points have valid values in the\n        attribute."], "extent": [1237, 1543]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "distmetric"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Apply Rolloff"], "extent": [1543, 1558], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["If ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Distance Metric"]}, " is ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Attribute"]}, ", apply a rolloff to the distance\n    output by treating the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Distance Attribute"]}, " as raw distances. A value\n    of zero will be fully transformed, while higher values will be\n    transformed less. Only points whose values are less than or equal to\n    ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Soft Radius"]}, " will be affected. If this is toggled off, the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Distance\n    Attribute"]}, " value is treated as if it has already been rolled off, and\n    the transform is multiplied by the value. A value of one will be fully\n    transformed while smaller values will be transformed less."], "extent": [1581, 2164]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "applyrolloff"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Distance Attribute"], "extent": [2164, 2184], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["If ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Distance Metric"]}, " is ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Attribute"]}, ", this specifies the point attribute\n    containing the values that modify the amount each point in the group is\n    transformed by. If ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Apply Rolloff"]}, " is true the values are treated as\n    raw distances and will be rolled off to between zero and one, otherwise\n    the transform amount is multiplied by the value."], "extent": [2203, 2563]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "distattr"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Soft Radius"], "extent": [2563, 2576], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Area of influence."], "extent": [2600, 2623]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channels": "/radius"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Soft type"], "extent": [2623, 2634], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The type of rolloff for soft modifications. This affects how\n    much influence your direct edits have on other points/faces\n    with the soft radius, based on their distance."], "extent": [2649, 2830]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Linear"], "extent": [2830, 2842], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Linear falloff: the amount of influence decreases\n        linearly with distance."], "extent": [2842, 2932]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Quadratic"], "extent": [2932, 2947], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Slow falloff: direct edits affect distant points/faces\n        more than with Cubic."], "extent": [2947, 3040]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Cubic"], "extent": [3040, 3051], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Quick falloff: direct edits affect distant points/faces\n        less than with Quadratic."], "extent": [3051, 3149]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Metaball"], "extent": [3149, 3163], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Calculate falloff according with the metaball density\n        function you specify in the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Kernel function"]}, "\n        parameter."], "extent": [3163, 3300]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "type"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Tangent Angles"], "extent": [3300, 3316], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Angles of the cubic rolloff function\u2019s tangents. The first value\n    applies to the tangent farthest from the source point, the\n    second applies to the tangent closest to the source point."], "extent": [3340, 3535]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"channels": "/tandeg"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Kernel Function"], "extent": [3535, 3552], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": null, "value": "/nodes/sop/metaball#kernels", "type": "link", "text": ["Metaball\n    kernel"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/metaball.html#kernels", "fragment": "#kernels"}, "  to use\n    when rolloff Type is ", {"type": "q", "text": ["Meta-ball"]}, "."], "extent": [3552, 3652]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Lead Point Attribute"], "extent": [3652, 3674], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["If ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Distance Metric"]}, " is ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Attribute"]}, " and ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Translate Along Lead Normal"]}, "\n    is true, this specifies the point attribute containing the point index\n    of the whose normal should be translated along. A value of -1 will cause\n    the point to be translated along its own normal."], "extent": [3695, 3980]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "leadptattr"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Translate Along Lead Normal"], "extent": [3980, 4009], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Translate points within the radius along the normal of the\n    point in Group closest to them. Otherwise translate along their\n    respective normals, giving a mushrooming effect."], "extent": [4009, 4193]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Recompute Point Normals"], "extent": [4193, 4218], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Recomputes point normals if they exist."], "extent": [4218, 4262]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Visualize Falloff"], "extent": [4262, 4281], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["When to output the soft radius falloff as a ", {"type": "code", "text": ["vis_falloff"]}, " point\n    attribute."], "extent": [4281, 4365]}, {"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Never"], "extent": [4365, 4376], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Never create or write to the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["vis_falloff"]}, " attribute."], "extent": [4376, 4438]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["Always"], "extent": [4438, 4450], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Always create and write to the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["vis_falloff"]}, " attribute. "], "extent": [4450, 4515]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["When Viewport Tool Is Active"], "extent": [4515, 4549], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Only create or write to the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["vis_falloff"]}, " attribute temporarily\n        when the viewport tool for this node is active."], "extent": [4549, 4686]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "text": "Parameters"}, {"level": 1, "id": "locals", "container": true, "type": "locals_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [4686, 4694], "body": [{"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["NPT"], "extent": [4694, 4703], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The number of points."], "extent": [4703, 4733]}], "container": true}, {"type": "dt", "indent": 4, "text": ["NPR"], "extent": [4733, 4742], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The number of primitives."], "extent": [4742, 4777]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "text": "Locals"}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [4777, 4786], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/peak", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/peak.html"}], "extent": [4786, 4808]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/softxform", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/softxform.html"}], "extent": [4808, 4835]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/xform", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/xform.html"}], "extent": [4835, 4858]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/clay", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/clay.html"}], "extent": [4858, 4880]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/point", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/point.html"}], "extent": [4880, 4903]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/falloff", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/falloff.html"}], "extent": [4903, 4929]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["Soft Peak"], "summary": ["Moves the selected point along its normal, with smooth rolloff to\nsurrounding points."]}